      <div resp="part:emfr" type="translation">
        <p n="1-3">
         		Fifteenth <supplied reason="subaudible">year</supplied> of the victorious king Indravarman.
         	</p>
        <p n="4-10">
         		Ātaṉ of Mēlūr <supplied reason="subaudible">is</supplied> he who died in a battle <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>pūcal</foreign>
          </supplied> which occurred <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>ōṭiṉa</foreign>
          </supplied> with the king <supplied reason="explanation">
            <foreign>aracarai</foreign>
            <note>Note the accusative, governed by <foreign>ōṭiṉa</foreign>.</note>
          </supplied> of Mīkoṉṟaināṭu.
         	</p>
      </div>
      <div type="commentary">
        <p>The Indravarman of the regnal year is probably one among the Pallava kings named Mahendravarman.</p>
      </div>
